#: ../../language/error_codes/E0027.md:1
msgid "E0027"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0027.md:3
msgid "Warning name: `deprecated_syntax`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0027.md:5
msgid ""
"The syntax is deprecated. Please refer to the warning message on the "
"reason and potential fix."
msgstr "语法已弃用。请参考警告消息，了解原因和潜在修复方法。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0027.md:8
msgid ""
"For example, one deprecated usage is declaring a polymorphic function as "
"`fn f[T]`. Instead, write the type parameters before the function name, "
"as in `fn[T] f`."
msgstr "例如，一种已弃用的用法是将多态函数声明为 `fn f[T]`。应改为将类型参数写在函数名之前，例如 `fn[T] f`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0027.md:12
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0027.md:14
msgid ""
"fn identity[T](value : T) -> T {\n"
"  //\n"
"  // Warning: The syntax fn f[..] for declaring polymorphic function is\n"
"  // deprecated. Use fn[..] f instead.\n"
"  value\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"fn main {\n"
"  println(identity(\"Hello, world!\"))\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0027.md:18
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0027.md:20
msgid ""
"Migrate the code according to the warning message. In this case, move the"
" type parameter list before the function name."
msgstr "根据警告信息迁移代码。在这种情况下，请将类型参数列表移动到函数名之前。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0027.md:23
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"fn[T] identity(value : T) -> T {\n"
"  value\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"fn main {\n"
"  println(identity(\"Hello, world!\"))\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
